[2] Contiki, &lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.contiki-os.org&quot;&gt;http://www.contiki-os.org&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Rocky Lim</name><email>rockylim@snu.ac.kr</email><uri>https://rockylim92.github.io/</uri></author><summary type="html">TI Sensortag CC2650 and Contiki</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="http://localhost:4000/%7B%22feature%22=%3Enil,%20%22teaser%22=%3E%22csiro_2_1.png%22%7D" /></entry></feed>